Components

Supports the following classes and lifetimes (when each component is available and destroyed):

# Componentname -> when is Created -> when is Destroyed

•  ApplicationComponent -> Application onCreate() -> Application onDestroy()
•  ActivityComponent ->  Activity onCreate() -> Activity onDestroy()
•  ActivityRetained Component -> Activity onCreate() -> Activity onDestroy()
•  FragmentComponent -> Fragment onAttach() -> Fragment onDestroy()
•  ViewComponent ->  View super() -> View destroyed
•  ViewWithFragmentComponent  -> View super()  -> View destroyed
•  ServiceComponent  -> Service onCreate()  -> Service onDestroy()